elements.name: Verify single item touch with iframes

steps.name: I read the file with the "profiles" and "singleItem"
I open login page
I fill username with of sendoso applicaton "afshan.shakoor@sendoso.com"
I fill password with of sendoso applicaton "Sendoso@123???"
I click on the submit button of second button
I close pop up button
I click on "Touches" Tab
I click on create New Touch button
I select "Single Items" touch under Inventoried Sends at index
I click on the next step of the create touch
I select "CypressProduct" product from existing items
I click on the next step of the create touch
I select charge cost to "Funding Source"
I select "QuotingCalculator FS" funding source to associate touch
I edit up the touchName "touchName" appearing at the page of enter touch details
